Review_Text:
I've absolutely loved this documentary! If you want to cry and laugh at the same time you've to watch it!Lewis Capaldi is such a beautiful soul... I've appreciated how funny and real he is and that he has embraced and showed to the world his vulnerabilities.Without talking about his enormous talent in singing and writing songs!It's a real backstage of his professional and private life.I also wanna thank him to give me and my boyfriend a little bit of courage to be more confident (our dream is to become singers too).I've just bought your tickets to see you on tour.Can't wait to see you in Milan
XX
